Package: google-chat-linux
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, xdg-desktop-portal
Description: Unofficial alternative Google Chat desktop app
 An unofficial Google Chat desktop application for Linux,
 built with Electron. Provides a native-feeling desktop
 experience for Google Chat with system tray support,
 desktop notifications, and protocol handler for gchat:// URLs.
